{"questionId":"1249677","questionHtml":"<p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">Light of wavelength <em>λ</em> is normally incident on a diffraction grating of spacing 3<em>λ</em>. What is the angle between the two second-order maxima?</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">A.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>sin</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac></math></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">B.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msup><mi>sin</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mfrac><mn>4</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac></math></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">C.&nbsp;&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mn>2</mn><msup><mi>sin</mi><mrow><mo>-</mo><mn>1</mn></mrow></msup><mfrac><mn>2</mn><mn>3</mn></mfrac></math></span></p>\n<p><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\"><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff;\">D.&nbsp; &gt;90° so no second orders appear</span></span></p>","markschemeHtml":"<p>C</p>","meta":{"questionId":"1249677","referenceCode":"19N.1A.HL.TZ0.28","subjectId":"59-dp-physics-first-assessment-2025","title":"Light of wavelength λ is normally incident on a diffraction grating of spacing 3λ. What is the angle between the two second-order maxima? A. sin-123 B. sin-143 C. 2sin-123 D. >90° ","paper":"1A","level":"HL","questionNumber":"28","marksAvailable":"[Maximum mark: 1]","breadcrumbLabels":["C. Wave behaviour","C.3 Wave phenomena"],"memberSectionIds":[],"sectionOrders":{}}}